clock.StopwatchApi.start_stopwatch.message: Error 500: Internal server error - Clock service encountered an unexpected error while starting stopwatch

Error 408: Request timeout - The stopwatch start request timed out. Please try again.
Error 429: Rate limit exceeded - Too many requests to the clock service. Please try again in a few seconds.
Error 403: Permission denied - Stopwatch access permission is required. Please grant stopwatch access permissions.
Error 500: System error - Operating system error occurred during stopwatch start. Please contact system administrator.
